import React, {useState} from "react";
import {Button, Card, Col, Container, Form, ListGroup, Row} from "react-bootstrap";
import DateTimePicker from 'react-datetime-picker';

import "react-datepicker/dist/react-datepicker.css";

class App extends React.Component {

    constructor(props) {
        super(props);
        this.state = {
            name: "",
            surname: "",
            phone: "",
            email: "",
            street: "",
            houseNumber: "",
            city: "",
            plate: "",
            date: ""
        };
    }

    onChange = (e, name) => {
        this.setState({
            [name]: e
        })
        console.log(this.state)
    }


    render() {

        return (

            <Container>
                <Card style={{
                    width:800,
                    border:0
                }}>
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Title style={{
                            display: "flex",
                            justifyContent: "center",
                            alignItems: "center"
                        }}>Registrace nové objednávky</Card.Title>
                        <Form>

                            <Row className="mt-3">
                                <Col>
                                    <Form.Group controlId="nameId">
                                        <Form.Control
                                            type="text"
                                            placeholder="např. Karel"
                                            value={this.state.name}
                                            onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'name')}
                                        />
                                    </Form.Group>
                                </Col>
                                <Col>
                                    <Form.Group controlId="surnameId">
                                        <Form.Control
                                            type="text"
                                            placeholder="např. Novák"
                                            value={this.state.surname}
                                            onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'surname')}
                                        />
                                    </Form.Group>
                                </Col>
                            </Row>

                            <Row className="mt-3">
                                <Col>
                                    <Form.Group controlId="phoneId">
                                        <Form.Control
                                            type="text"
                                            placeholder="např. 605312434"
                                            value={this.state.phone}
                                            onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'phone')}
                                        />
                                    </Form.Group>
                                </Col>
                                <Col>
                                    <Form.Group controlId="emailId">
                                        <Form.Control
                                            type="text"
                                            placeholder="např. karelnovak@seznam.cz"
                                            value={this.state.email}
                                            onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'email')}
                                        />
                                    </Form.Group>
                                </Col>
                            </Row>

                            <Row>
                                <Col>
                                    <Row className="mt-3">
                                        <Form.Group controlId="streetId">
                                            <Form.Control
                                                type="text"
                                                placeholder="např. Dlouhá"
                                                value={this.state.street}
                                                onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'street')}
                                            />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-3">
                                        <Form.Group controlId="houseNumberId">
                                            <Form.Control
                                                type="text"
                                                placeholder="např. 5568"
                                                value={this.state.houseNumber}
                                                onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'houseNumber')}
                                            />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-3">
                                        <Form.Group controlId="cityId">
                                            <Form.Control
                                                type="text"
                                                placeholder="např. Praha"
                                                value={this.state.description}
                                                onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'city')}
                                            />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                </Col>

                                <Col>
                                    <Row className="mt-3">
                                        <Form.Group controlId="plateId">
                                            <Form.Control
                                                type="text"
                                                placeholder="např. 1T23456"
                                                value={this.state.description}
                                                onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e.target.value, 'plate')}
                                            />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-3">
                                        <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.SelectCustom">
                                            <Form.Control as="select" custom>
                                                <option>CAR</option>
                                                <option>VAN</option>
                                                <option>TRUCK</option>
                                            </Form.Control>
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-3">
                                        <Form.Group controlId="startWorkId">
                                            <DateTimePicker
                                                onChange={(e) => this.onChange(e, 'date')}
                                                value={this.state.date}
                                            />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                </Col>
                            </Row>

                            <Row className="m-3">
                                <Col>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="pneu" label="Pneumatiky"/>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="oil" label="Výměna oleje"/>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="battery" label="Baterie"/>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="ac" label="Klimatizace"/>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="wiper" label="Stěrače"/>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="complete" label="Kompletní servis"/>
                                    </Row>
                                    <Row className="mt-1">
                                        <Form.Check type="geometry" label="Geometrie"/>
                                    </Row>
                                </Col>
                                <Col>
                                    <Row>
                                        <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect2">
                                            <Form.Control as="select" multiple>
                                                <option>1</option>
                                                <option>2</option>
                                                <option>3</option>
                                                <option>4</option>
                                                <option>5</option>
                                            </Form.Control>
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Row>
                                </Col>
                            </Row>

                            <Row>
                                <Col style={{display: 'flex',  justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center'}}>
                                    <Button variant="primary" onClick={this.createNew} type="submit">Uložit</Button>
                                </Col>
                            </Row>

                        </Form>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
            </Container>
        );
    }
}

export default App;
